name: KITC / SENTO SINJING
description: This is Sinjing the Shiba Inu from KITC. Take a break, have a relaxing bath with Sinjing to replenish your energy and mental resources. This bath is open for everybody, even superhero, warrior, princess, and any kind of people need a break now and then. Unplug and relax. KITC, your daily dose of happiness.
